        modalAdditionalInfo="Hydrogram is a Telegram MTProto API framework written in Python, based on the popular Pyrogram library, with a completely reworked and optimised codebase.<br>It's the base for all our projects that need the Telegram API."
        githubLink="https://github.com/hydrogram/hydrogram"
