        description="Python module to search on DuckDuckGo."
        modalAdditionalInfo="Duckpy is a simple Python module for searching on the DuckDuckGo website.<br>It offers sync and async APIs, proxy support and has a simple API."
        githubLink="https://github.com/AmanoTeam/duckpy"
